      • zeroPad

        public static java.lang.String zeroPad​(int num,
                                       int totalDigits)
        Supplement zeros before some number.
        参数:
        num - number to be processed.
        totalDigits - how many digits including zeros.
        返回:
        a string.

      • checkUserIDPassword

        public static int checkUserIDPassword​(java.lang.String type,
                                      java.lang.String id,
                                      java.lang.String password)
                               throws java.lang.Exception
        Check user inputs: username (email or phone no.) and password.
        参数:
        type - id_type.
        id - email, phone no. or member no.
        password - string from JPasswordField.
        返回:
        1 if both username and password correct; -1 if password incorrect; 0 if username not found and -2 if something missing.
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception

      • isValidEmail

        public static boolean isValidEmail​(java.lang.String email)
        Check if an email address is valid or invalid. See reference: https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/check-email-address-valid-not-java/ See TDD case: "./tests/RegistrationTest"
        参数:
        email - address.
        返回:
        Boolean.

      • isPositiveNumeric

        public static boolean isPositiveNumeric​(java.lang.String text)
        Check if a text is a positive integer or float.

        Example -- true: 1.5, 6, 3.14 false: -1.3, asd, 3.x
        参数:
        text - String to be tested
        返回:
        true if passed otherwise false

      • MD5EncryptedPassword

        public static java.lang.String MD5EncryptedPassword​(java.lang.String password)
                                             throws java.lang.Exception
        Get MD5 encrypted password.
        参数:

        返回:
        Encrypted String.
        抛出:

      • saveStringToTextFile

        public static void saveStringToTextFile​(java.lang.String string,

        参数:
        string - Contents to be saved.
        path - File path.

      • openTextFile

        public static void openTextFile​(java.lang.String path)
                         throws java.lang.Exception
        Open Text file in os. See reference: https://www.yiibai.com/java/java-open-file.html
        参数:
        path - Text file path.
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception - if file doesn't exist or the OS cannot support opening txt file.
